{"tid":2341432,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以食到人地條仔","createTime":"2020-12-26T10:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T10:53:47.000Z","uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"817e14ad743ce1a2c0f80f88f4656c064c08cfb3","tid":2341432,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"最近係網上識左條仔,有仔既<br />\n同居緊但係佢地成日鬧交冷戰<br />\n成日都會同我呻唔開心<br />\n佢地既性生活都好唔協調<br />\n因為條仔好快射所以都好少搞野<br />\n但係我探過佢口風<br />\n佢又好似唔想出黎偷食<br />\n究竟點先可以食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e7870515644187da884157b5a26e958af11a0b","tid":2341432,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"@人怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b2179aca736d81322cd24aa0cdebcb132fd8c2","tid":2341432,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"3p咪食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9505bced74621dd2938cc7b3882f6c99aafaeab9","tid":2341432,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0b2179aca736d81322cd24aa0cdebcb132fd8c2","tid":2341432,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"3p咪食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"我們是好兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb38da63aa8511c42af71b66339ae7d4827f79cd","tid":2341432,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"0ce7a246b80b0338b74e72ad7a4391e20083a903","tid":2341432,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb38da63aa8511c42af71b66339ae7d4827f79cd","tid":2341432,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b191a8dff79a4f990a39b7703b6489adb0bf5a99","tid":2341432,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"白銀御行(有春袋)#370062 四大罪狀 歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n1. 利用白銀御行嘅名周圍開噁心/冇内容/抄襲嘅po同留噁心/冇内容/抄襲嘅回覆 負面影響動畫輝夜姬想讓人告白<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ac51NWD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAc51NWD.jpg&h=64c816bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n亦有唔少人認同<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWY3gB5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWY3gB5.png&h=cd50b07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 佢係on9仔濟癲嘅狗 濟癲條道友發表完偉論比人屌到自殺 而會員#370062係濟癲嘅狗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBYKLNa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBYKLNa.png&h=3b8c2c25&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.五毛級言論: 你唔搞其他人?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxRwqJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxRwqJX.png&h=f2693a69&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講得好 連登就係多得佢 木耳 飲L乜撚M依幾條<strong><strong><span class=\"red\">當連登係FB玩嘅死狗公</span></strong></strong>唔少<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoZJ1iP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoZJ1iP.jpg&h=ab6c268d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQcSUDQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQcSUDQ.png&h=7000e983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 恥笑毒撚 佢主人濟癲 老死浮雲 多次恥笑毒撚 話毒撚社會垃圾 反社會人渣 同依班人為伍嘅會員#370062都唔好得去邊 明明自己都係毒撚 正一25仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYD3gS1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYD3gS1.png&h=ac29add3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brgsJxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrgsJxB.png&h=0d69bccc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https:/